---

Portions of this software are derived from the following MIT-licensed
projects by jglim:

  * UnlockECU — https://github.com/jglim/UnlockECU
    (seed-key security-access algorithms ported in backend/mb/unlock.py;
    ECU definitions database db.json fetched by tools/fetch_unlock_db.py)

  * CaesarSuite — https://github.com/jglim/CaesarSuite
    (partial ports of the Caesar CBF container format in
    tools/caesar_comparam.py and tools/caesar_vc.py)

The J2534 driver build script (tools/build_driver_macos.sh) builds the
open-source driver from https://github.com/dschultzca/j2534.

This repository contains NO proprietary Mercedes-Benz data. CBF/CFF/VSG
files, derived databases and StarFinder archives are user-supplied and
excluded from version control (see .gitignore).
